--- PART 1: FOURIER STRUCTURE OF S ---
For circulant tournaments, |S_hat(t)|^2 = Q_t determines the eigenvalue structure.
Flat spectrum (Paley at p=3 mod 4) -> uniform eigenvalues -> rich cycle structure.

